graph LR
    DSPO[Data Science Pipelines Operator<br/>v0.0.1]

    %% External Dependencies (Required)
    DSPO -->|container orchestration| K8s["Kubernetes / OpenShift 4.11+"]
    DSPO -->|workflow execution| Argo["Argo Workflows v3.4+"]
    DSPO -->|artifact storage| S3["S3-compatible Object Storage"]

    %% External Dependencies (Optional)
    DSPO -.->|dev/test DB| MariaDBDep["MariaDB 10.3"]
    DSPO -.->|dev/test storage| MinioDep["Minio"]
    DSPO -.->|client SDK| KFPSDK["Kubeflow Pipelines SDK 2.x"]
    DSPO -.->|legacy DSPv1| Tekton["OpenShift Pipelines / Tekton 1.8+"]

    %% Internal ODH/RHOAI Dependencies
    DSPO -->|UI integration| Dashboard["ODH/RHOAI Dashboard"]
    DSPO -->|CR management| ODHOperator["ODH Operator /<br/>DataScienceCluster"]
    DSPO -->|model deployment| KServe["KServe"]
    DSPO -->|pipeline authoring| Workbenches["Workbenches<br/>(Notebooks)"]
    DSPO -.->|mTLS/traffic mgmt| ServiceMesh["Service Mesh<br/>(Istio)"]
    DSPO -->|metrics| Monitoring["OpenShift Monitoring<br/>(Prometheus)"]

    %% Integration Points
    Dashboard -->|UI mgmt| DSPO
    Workbenches -->|submit pipelines| DSPO
    ODHOperator -->|deploys/manages| DSPO

    %% Pipeline execution integration
    DSPO -->|integration| KServe
    DSPO -->|integration| Ray["Ray Clusters"]

    %% External services for pipeline pods
    DSPO -->|container images| Registry["Container Registries<br/>registry.redhat.io"]
    DSPO -.->|production DB| ExternalDB["External MySQL/<br/>PostgreSQL"]

    %% Certificates
    DSPO -->|pod-to-pod TLS| OpenShiftCerts["OpenShift Service-Serving<br/>Certificates"]

